items.title: Awesome Love2d
items.content_text:
### Distribution

*   [boon (⭐152)](https://github.com/camchenry/boon) - Multi-platform, easy to use tool supporting Windows, macOS, Linux.
*   [love-release (⭐482)](https://github.com/MisterDA/love-release) - A Lua script that automates game distribution. Supports Windows, macOS, Debian, Linux.
*   [makelove (⭐174)](https://github.com/pfirsich/makelove) - Advanced multi-platform tool to fuse your game written in Python 3. Supports Windows and Linux with AppImage.
items.content_html:

  • boon (⭐152) - Multi-platform, easy to use tool supporting Windows, macOS, Linux.
  • love-release (⭐482) - A Lua script that automates game distribution. Supports Windows, macOS, Debian, Linux.
  • makelove (⭐174) - Advanced multi-platform tool to fuse your game written in Python 3. Supports Windows and Linux with AppImage.

items.title: Awesome Fastapi
items.content_text:
### Utils / Other Tools

*   [FastAPI Websocket Pub/Sub (⭐16)](https://github.com/authorizon/fastapi_websocket_pubsub) - The classic pub/sub pattern made easily accessible and scalable over the web and across your cloud in realtime.
*   [FastAPI Websocket RPC (⭐8)](https://github.com/authorizon/fastapi_websocket_rpc) - RPC (bidirectional JSON RPC) over Websockets made easy, robust, and production ready.
